{"tid":1520414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察 趁早洗白","createTime":"2019-08-30T19:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T12:44:27.000Z","uid":40318,"like":389,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"42cc881044419ec45d86f518cfce612f1b000af8","tid":1520414,"uid":40318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:16:43.000Z","msg":"香港警察<br />\n你地都見今晚場大龍鳳 疑點多到一頁post都數唔哂<br />\n幾時開始 你地入餐廳買個外賣都要包住件褸<br />\n你地依三個月以嚟搏盡老命 捨棄尊嚴保護嘅政府<br />\n佢地今晚 為咗贏依場杖<br />\n不惜請外人斬你地手足 當你地係棄子<br />\n就算你當我地係曱甴 起碼我地都唔可能咁樣出賣自己手足<br />\n今鑊你地唔係忍呀話<br />\n今晚佢為政治目的斬一件<br />\n他朝到你或者你屋企人被斬都唔出奇<br />\n你同我都清楚中聯辦 港共 鄉黑係無人性<br />\n你地自己衡量吓 <br />\n我唔講乜柒良唔良知<br />\n解放軍 有軍火架生嘅鄉黑唔敢明刀明鎗打市民 就唯有搵你地同你地家屬開拖拎民意<br />\n我身邊都有同學係警察仔女<br />\n我知道你地仔女政見同你地未必一致 但我諗你地都唔會想中聯辦下個order目標就係你地屋企人<br />\n依家係中聯辦同港共要搞你地/警察家屬去拎光環<br />\n你當係保護你地屋企人 你地係咪要企出嚟推翻依個草菅人命 麻木不仁嘅港共政權<br />\n或者 可能你都唔滿意政府好耐<br />\n警察變節並唔可恥 睇吓烏克蘭革命 變節警察係人民英雄<br />\n希望有一日可以見到你地係上哂full gear好型咁企係市民嗰邊 同一陣線<br />\n只有你地企出嚟 你地可以抬起頭做人<br />\n出街唔駛再俾人當過街老鼠<br />\n細路見到你地唔再係驚<br />\n<br />\n市民原唔原諒你地係後話<br />\n至少當刻唔好俾政府鄉黑聯手搞你地手足/屋企人"},{"pid":"ab5dba9065cf165a587528fb581a01c9b8588134","tid":1520414,"uid":33930,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:17:04.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=f93306c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=9033536e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=6733beab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=36e8e93e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293</a></span>"},{"pid":"dfe928fd20fd8c99cb58c673e6bd1e5882a467d7","tid":1520414,"uid":40318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:17:38.000Z","msg":"推俾mon post差佬睇"},{"pid":"b3541f4f83e2df97e6919cc45bf565d83eb736b5","tid":1520414,"uid":260653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:17:51.000Z","msg":"唉 佢地唔識醒"},{"pid":"57206a5727bec5136a8f5ec41a6ad86209fc52e4","tid":1520414,"uid":231583,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:18:29.000Z","msg":"仲趁咩早洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2014後已經無得洗白啦<br />\n何況而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a6e2119dbedd90fe56db25a93e50db39e4cd82","tid":1520414,"uid":264457,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:19:23.000Z","msg":"推你老母，講埋啲